# ValuePacket — one-command local demo
# Regenerate with: vhs demo.tape
Output demo.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 13
Set Width 1100
Set Height 700
Set Theme "Oceanic-Next"
Set Padding 24
Set Framerate 12
Set PlaybackSpeed 1

Sleep 1s

Type "make demo-local"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Sleep 28s
Sleep 3s
